Package: scTrends
Title: Trend Detection for Single-Cell Pseudotime Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jianbo", "Qing", email = "Dr.jianboqing@email.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools to bin single-cell expression along pseudotime, 
    automatically tune trend-detection parameters, classify gene trends, 
    and visualize expression trajectories.
